persons: Elizabeth II, Queen of Great Britain
subject: Horse Racing
lead_paragraph: Queen Elizabeth’s horse Estimate won the Royal Ascot Gold Cup. It was the first time a reigning monarch’s horse had claimed victory in the race’s 207-year history.
